Class InnerLabel

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pepstock.charba.client.commons.NativeObjectContainer
      • org.pepstock.charba.client.commons.AbstractNode

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HasLabel, HasTextStrokeOptions, IsDefaultsInnerLabel, IsDefaultsLabelHandler, IsDefaultsTextStrokeOptionsHandler, IsScriptableFontProvider<AnnotationContext>, IsScriptablePaddingProvider<AnnotationContext>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractBoxedLabel, LineLabel
    abstract class InnerLabel
extends AbstractNode
implements IsDefaultsInnerLabel, HasLabel, HasTextStrokeOptions
    base object to map all label options for instances which belongs to another container.
    Author:
    Andrea "Stock" Stocchero
